  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Shared-Desktop-Ontologies</title>

    <para>The Shared desktop ontologies provide RDF vocabularies for the Semantic Desktop. This includes basic ontologies like RDF and RDFS and all the Nepomuk ontologies like NRL, NIE, or NFO which are also maintained and developed in this open-source project.</para>

    &lfs70_checked;

